    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been reliably maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior is clean but does show some minor road wear, such as small stone chips on the hood and a few light surface scratches consistent with its age. Inside, the cabin is well-kept; the upholstery is intact and free of tears, though there is some light creasing on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car is sound, starts up without hesitation, and all major electronics and climate control systems are fully functional. It is a dependable driver that offers a comfortable ride and is ready for its next owner without any immediate repairs needed.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
